<l>iyalpiṉā ṉilvāḻkkai vāḻpava ṉeṉpāṉ</l>
<l>muyalvāru ḷellān talai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is he who lives the household life with integrity</l>
<l>who is chief among all those who strive.</l>
